rules.description: Map Left Command + Delete to Option + Delete
Double-tap Left Command to set Launcher mode

manipulators.description: to_delayed_action is set to 5000ms in karabiner.json

rules.description: Launcher (Open): press keys to launch apps

to.shell_command: osascript -e 'tell application "System Events"' -e 'if (name of first application process whose frontmost is true) is "CLion" then' -e 'tell application process "CLion" to set visible to false' -e 'else' -e 'do shell script "open -a \"CLion\""' -e 'end if' -e 'end tell'
